original_font_information.description: Fell Types - English size - Roman. Typeface from the  types bequeathed in 1686 to the University of Oxford by John Fell. Originally cut by Christoffel van Dijck. To be printed at 13.5 points to match the original size. Autospaced and autokerned using iKern developed by Igino Marini.
